headline: D.R. Horton (NYSE:DHI) Expands Into Farms Of New Kent With 45 New Townhomes
summary: D.R. Horton (NYSE:DHI) recently entered into an agreement to develop 45 townhomes in the Farms of New Kent community, signaling business expansion efforts as construction is set to commence soon. Despite this positive development, the company's share price remained flat over the last week amidst broader market volatility, which saw a 4% decline due to fluctuating earnings reports and tariff concerns.
